DoubleSetting
public static final class DoubleSetting.Builder extends com.google.protobuf.GeneratedMessage.Builder<DoubleSetting.Builder> implements DoubleSettingOrBuilder
UI definition for a floating-point number setting.
Used to render decimal number input fields with precision control.
Supports range limits, step increments, and decimal formatting options.
Protobuf type soulfire.v1.DoubleSetting
